name: A night out in Torquay vol. 1

metadata.name: A night out in Torquay vol 1 #1/100
metadata.description:
A night out in Torquay vol.1 is a dream sequence short story; an Otherworlds trip into town to see the Torquay lights and stroll along the prom.

This NFT zine was photographed, conceived, chronologically sequenced, designed, minted and released for sale in just over 24 hours.
